+    )}, SD ${fmt(results.ySd)}). I ran 25 propose-test-refine iterations covering univariate main effects, all-feature multivariable adjustment, interaction models, stratified subgroup checks, a quadratic check for feature_044, and level-specific contrasts for feature_027. P-values use large-sample normal approximations to OLS/Welch statistics.`
